cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.GR 

This paper deals with object recognition using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) and object detection algorithms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of rendering techniques and active learning, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The experiments involve training algorithms for object detection, which falls under robotics (cs.RO) and graphics (cs.GR).
